OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will be dry this
OL,6,Fmorning with some sunshine. Remaining
OL,7,Fdry and sunny through this afternoon.
OL,8,FWarm, locally very warm across western
OL,9,FFermanagh. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be mainly dry but the
OL,14,Fodd shower possible later on.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry day with variable
OL,17,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
