OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart with the odd shower on Friday,
OL,7,Fthen dry and brighter by afternoon.
OL,8,FCloudy on Saturday with outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain. Mainly dry on Sunday.
